Package: area
Title: Calculate Area of Triangles and Polygons
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Sumner",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2471-7511"))
Description: Calculate the area of triangles and polygons using the shoestring 
 formula. Area may be signed, taking into account path orientation, or unsigned, 
 ignoring path orientation. 
